So you know space is mostly made from unburned stellar mass that turns into vast sheets of carbon monoxide gathered around Stars.

When the 6 and 8 electron shells from that carbon and oxygen refuses to fill the center, but instead tricks the stellar mass into balancing it... Guess what element they 14estly turn into!

Silica. Sand.

Jupiter is surrounded by tons of masses that have refused to contribute to center, and the space between those Stars and failed stars is behaving as something that consumes but never becomes the center.

.

Now this is INTERESTING if you are aware that plantlife is the living relationship between two large centers of gravity.

Roots seek into the soil, growing INWARD towards the center of the planet we stand on.

Branches and leaves reach up towards the warm light of the star we orbit. Growing INWARD to the center of our star system itself.

Plants are made of materials that are CENTERED.

The carbon monoxide material of space and the barren wasteland moons that clutter our star system ARE THE OPPOSITE... feeding upon the center.

And that smoke and sand isn't thinking like and CERTAINLY NOT behaving like an angel of the garden.

.

Jupiter may WANT to consume everything but Angels of the garden, but the space between masses CLEARLY HAS OTHER OPINIONS.

this is the same smoke that u.v. passes thru, on its way to making melanin in the darkest animals.

And it's not ever explained to people what the REAL difference between black and white people is...

If it's only "protecting animals who've been OUTSIDE in the sun a lot"... WHY is the smoke of space eating the plant-growing stellar centers... And instead keeping selfish animals alive that the light would rather burn to death?

It's quite a thing.

When those dark desert cultures get to live unchallenged by the soil they stand on, guess what happens?

The light acts like it thinks MEN are "angels of the garden" protecting and growing helpless flowers called women.

But because the carbon monoxide influenced, uncentered soil is serving the needs of the women instead of growing plants... it's not feeding it's dirty soil INTO the women, it's INSTEAD growing big muscular men by FIGHTING with the light that tries to teach them to be great Angels.

Women, free of all pressure.

Served by soil and men.

Men who are still challenged by the light to be angels and by the smoke and sand... to be selfish.
